cat << EOF
Ethtool is a Linux net driver diagnostic and tuning tool for the
Linux series of kernels. It obtains information and diagnostics
related to media, link status, driver version, PCI (or other) bus
location, and more. Ethtool obsoletes mii-tool.
EOF
